                             @{b}@{u} PICK UPS @{ub}@{uu}


     Extra life: Eerrmmm...guess

     Extra energy: : )

     Pills:  "P" more power
             "R" more range
             "E" extra bullets

     The pills are not compatible IE you can not have extra range and
     extra power at the same time.Likewise,they are not accumulative,which
     means that if you pick twice the same pill,it won't have a double
     effect on your weapon.
     Pill's effects are lost when you move into a new chapter.

     Look at the "Help" sub-menu to see what the pick ups look like!

