                           @{b}@{u} SOME TIPS @{ub}@{uu}


       1-Remember that you can shoot your weapon in any direction!That's
         absolutely vital later on!

       2-Sometimes crawling is the only way of avoiding enemy's bullets.

       3-There are lots of hidden extra lives and energy to be found.If you
         are to make it to the end,you'll need them.

       4-As in Charly,it does not pay to be fancy.If the enemy is giving you
         an horrendous beating,then you better run away!!


